8 POLICY COMMITTEE RECOMMENDATION
9 An Act relating to motor vehicles; amending 47 O.S.
2021, Section 10-118, which relates to accident
10 response fee prohibited; prohibiting the charging of
certain fee for accident response by certain
11 entities; making certain exception; and providing an
effective date.
12
13
14
15 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
16 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 47 O.S. 2021, Section 10-118, is
17 amended to read as follows:
18 Section 10-118. A. Notwithstanding any other section of law to
19 the contrary, no person or entity shall impose an accident response
20 fee for the response or investigation of a motor vehicle accident by
21 law enforcement, fire department, or municipality; provided,
22 however, that this prohibition shall not apply to a volunteer fire
23 department.
24
Req. No. 16545 Page 1

1 B. For purposes of this section, “accident response fee” means
2 a fee imposed for the response or investigation of a motor vehicle
3 accident and does not mean any fee otherwise specifically authorized
4 by law.
5 SECTION 2. This act shall become effective November 1, 2026.
